msgid "0:希の本社ビルは渋谷駅から歩いて行ける場所にあるらしい。[linebreak]でも、僕の精神力はそのビルにたどり着く前に根こそぎ奪い取られそうだった。[%p]"
msgstr "0:The Nozomi HQ building was within walking distance of Shibuya Station. But my mental strength felt like I was going to run out before I got there.[%p]"

msgid "100:なにしろセナは、本気で僕を鎖でぐるぐる巻きにしたまま、渋谷のど真ん中を練り歩いているんだから。[%p]"
msgstr "100:Sena was walking right through the middle of the city with me wrapped up in a chain behind her.[%p]"

msgid "200:大量のケータイカメラが僕に向けられたのは言うまでもない。[linebreak]これでまた僕の黒歴史がひとつ増えたよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "200:Of course, there were any number of people with their phones pointed at us. As if I hadn't been humiliated enough already.[%p]"

msgid "300:きっともうすでに、＠ちゃんではこんなスレが立っているに違いない。[%p]"
msgstr "300:There were probably threads up on @chan already.[%p]"

msgid "400:[name]エスパー[line]西條が渋谷で黒髪美人にわんわんプレイされてた[%p]"
msgstr "400:[name]エスパー[line]Boy Psychic Nishijo, doing human pet play with a black-haired hottie in the middle of Shibuya.[%p]"

msgid "500:うう、またＤＱＮどもにいじめられる……。[%p]"
msgstr "500:The DQNs were going to tease me again.[%p]"

msgid "600:僕が何度懇願しても、セナは鎖を外してはくれなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "600:I kept begging, but Sena wouldn't take the chains off.[%p]"

msgid "700:[name]セナ[line]「今のお前にとって必要なのは、目立つことだ。今のところ、その目的は達成されてるだろう？」[%p]"
msgstr "700:[name]セナ[line]What you need to do now is stand out. And you're certainly standing out now, aren't you?[%p]"

msgid "800:などと、意味不明の理屈を振りかざしてくる。[linebreak]いったいどういう理屈なんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "800:I had no idea what the hell she was talking about. What did that mean?[%p]"

msgid "900:“[color index="A0FF0000"]安西先生[color index="800000"]、目立つ男になりたいです……”[linebreak]なんて頼んだ覚えは、これっぽっちもないのに！[%p]"
msgstr "900:I'd never in my life said, “[color index="A0FF0000"]Coach Anzai[color index="800000"], I want to be a man who stands out!”[%p]"

msgid "1000:しかも敵の本拠地に乗り込むなんて、いつ殺されてもおかしくないんだぞ！[%p]"
msgstr "1000:And we were heading into the enemy HQ, too. We could be killed at any moment![%p]"

msgid "1100:そんな僕の訴えを、セナはことごとく無視した。[linebreak]鎖を引いたまま、おしゃれなビルへと入っていく。[linebreak]引っ張られ、僕もその後に付いていかざるを得なかった。[%p]"
msgstr "1100:But Sena ignored my pleas. She went inside a fancy-looking building, still holding the chain in her hand. I was literally dragged along behind her.[%p]"

msgid "1200:目の前に広がる受付ロビーの豪華さに、僕は息を呑む。[%p]"
msgstr "1200:I gasped when I saw how fancy the lobby in front of me was.[%p]"

msgid "1300:希グループ。[%p]"
msgstr "1300:The Nozomi Group.[%p]"

msgid "1400:いまや日本を代表する[color index="A0FF0000"]コングロマリット[color index="800000"]って聞いた。[linebreak]僕みたいなヘタレ学生の日常とは、あまりにもかけ離れた世界。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:It was supposedly one of Japan's biggest corporate [color index="A0FF0000"]conglomerates[color index="800000"] right now. It was a world apart from the daily life of a wimpy schoolkid like me.[%p]"

msgid "1500:こんなビルに足を踏み入れた経験なんてないから、ロビーの広さとか、受付のおねいさんたちがリアルに鎮座していることに、僕はたじろいでしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:I'd never been inside a building like this before, and the size of the lobby, and the pretty girls sitting motionlessly at the reception desk, staggered me.[%p]"

msgid "1600:そもそも、ここって会社だろ……。[linebreak]関係者以外立ち入り禁止なんじゃないの？[%p]"
msgstr "1600:This was a corporate office, right? Wasn't it supposed to be off limits to the public?[%p]"

msgid "1700:僕もセナも、翠明の制服を着ている。どう見ても高校生。[linebreak]しかも１人は鎖を巻かれてるっていう不審者丸出しの格好。[linebreak]にもかかわらず正面から堂々と入っていけるセナの神経を疑う。[%p]"
msgstr "1700:Both Sena and I were wearing a Suimei uniform. We were clearly both high school kids, and one of us was a weirdo with a chain wrapped around him. I didn't understand how Sena could walk right in like she owned the place. Was she just crazy?[%p]"

msgid "1800:案の定、正面玄関の自動ドアをくぐった瞬間に、受付のおねいさんと目が合った。[%p]"
msgstr "1800:Of course, when we went through the automatic doors and saw the receptionists, their eyes met ours.[%p]"

msgid "1900:[name]拓巳[line]「か、帰ろうよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "1900:[name]拓巳[line]L-Let's go home.[%p]"

msgid "2000:これ以上進むのを躊躇した。[linebreak]だけどセナは止まらない。[%p]"
msgstr "2000:I hesitated to go any further. But Sena didn't stop.[%p]"

msgid "2100:[name]セナ[line]「心配するな」[%p]"
msgstr "2100:[name]セナ[line]Don't worry.[%p]"

msgid "2200:受付を通り過ぎて、さらに奥のエレベーターホールへ。[linebreak]誰にもなにも言われなかった……。いったい、なんで……？[%p]"
msgstr "2200:We walked past the front desk and into the elevator hall. Nobody said a word. Why?[%p]"

msgid "2300:セナはエレベーターには乗ろうとしなかった。[linebreak]ホールの近くにあった防火扉を開けて入っていく。[linebreak]中は薄暗い非常階段で、そこでセナはようやく足を止めた。[%p]"
msgstr "2300:Sena didn't get in one of the elevators. She opened the emergency exit near the elevator hall. There was a dimly lit emergency staircase inside. Only after we were there did she stop.[%p]"

msgid "2400:[name]セナ[line]「周囲は、私たちを希の社員だと思い込んでる」[%p]"
msgstr "2400:[name]セナ[line]Everyone around us thinks we work here.[%p]"

msgid "2500:いつの間にか、身体を圧迫するような感触がなくなっていた。[linebreak]見ると、ぐるぐるに巻き付いていた鎖がきれいさっぱり消滅している。そしてセナの手には、ディソード。[%p]"
msgstr "2500:The sense of something pressing up against my body had vanished. I looked and saw that the chain wrapping around me had disappeared. And now Sena was holding her Di-Sword in her hand.[%p]"

msgid "2600:やっぱりあの鎖は、ギガロマニアックスの力でリアルブートされた妄想……だったのか？[%p]"
msgstr "2600:That chain was a real booted delusion, then?[%p]"

msgid "2700:で、セナが僕の目のデッドスポットに反粒子を送り込んだことで、そのリアルブートされた鎖が今度は一瞬で消えた……？[%p]"
msgstr "2700:And then, the chain Sena had real booted by sending anti-particles into the dead spots of my eyes suddenly disappeared.[%p]"

msgid "2800:[name]拓巳[line]「の、希の社員と思ってるって、ど、どういう……」[%p]"
msgstr "2800:[name]拓巳[line]W-What do you mean they think we work for Nozomi?[%p]"

msgid "2900:[name]セナ[line]「そう思い込ませた。肉眼で私たちを見た人間全員にな」[%p]"
msgstr "2900:[name]セナ[line]I'm making them believe it. The effect extends to everyone who sees us with the naked eye.[%p]"

msgid "3000:思い込ませた、だって……？[linebreak]そんなこともできるのか？[%p]"
msgstr "3000:Making them believe it? Was that possible?[%p]"

msgid "3100:と、セナは階段の上を振り仰いだ。[linebreak]そこには、監視カメラらしきものが設置されている。赤いランプが付いていて、不気味な音を立てながら首を振っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "3100:Sena looked up toward the top of the stairs. What looked like a security camera was waiting there. There was a red light on it, and it was scanning from right to left while making an eerie noise.[%p]"

msgid "3200:[name]拓巳[line]「か、監視カメラにも……思い込ませることって、で、できるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "3200:[name]拓巳[line]C-Can you make a security camera believe it, too?[%p]"

msgid "3300:[name]セナ[line]「やろうと思えばできるかもな。試したことはない。それにやる必要もない」[%p]"
msgstr "3300:[name]セナ[line]I could if I wanted to, maybe. I've never tried it. And I don't need to it.[%p]"

msgid "3400:[name]拓巳[line]「な、なんで！？\u3000ば、ば、バレちゃうじゃないか！」[%p]"
msgstr "3400:[name]拓巳[line]W-Why? T-They'll find us![%p]"

msgid "3500:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、あり得ない……。す、す、[color index="A0FF0000"]スニーキングミッション[color index="800000"]では、監視カメラは最初に壊すでしょ、常識的に考えて……」[%p]"
msgstr "3500:[name]拓巳[line]You're crazy! I-In [color index="A0FF0000"]stealth missions[color index="800000"], the first thing you do is always destroy the security cameras![%p]"

msgid "3600:ゲームの知識だけど。[%p]"
msgstr "3600:At least, that's what I'd learned from video games.[%p]"

msgid "3700:[name]セナ[line]「言っただろう。お前が目立つことが必要なんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "3700:[name]セナ[line]I told you. You need to stand out.[%p]"

msgid "3800:だから、意味が分からないってば。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:I had no idea what she meant.[%p]"

msgid "3900:矛盾してるじゃないか。“希の社員だと思い込ませた”っていうカモフラージュ方法を取りながら、“目立つことが必要”なんてさ。[linebreak]結局どっちなんだ？\u3000なにがしたいんだ？[%p]"
msgstr "3900:She was contradicting herself, wasn't she? She wanted to camouflage us by making everyone believe we were Nozomi employees, but I also needed to stand out? Which was it? What was she trying to accomplish here?[%p]"

msgid "4000:誰も彼も、思わせぶりなことしか言おうとしない。[linebreak]僕を、バカにしてるのか！？\u3000どうせ言ったって西條拓巳は理解できないだろうとか、思ってるのか！？[%p]"
msgstr "4000:No one ever explained to me what the hell they were actually talking about. Did they all think I was stupid? Did they all just think there was no point in telling Takumi Nishijo, since he wouldn't be able to understand it?[%p]"

msgid "4100:うう、くそぅ、僕は、頭はいいんだぞ……。[linebreak]絶対に、ＩＱじゃセナより上だね。間違いない。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:Gah... I was smart, damn it! My IQ was definitely higher than Sena's. I was sure of it.[%p]"

msgid "4200:唇を噛んで、悔しさを我慢している僕を差し置いて、セナはさっさと１人で階段を上っていった。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:While I stood there, biting my lip in frustration, Sena began to walk up the stairs herself.[%p]"

msgid "4300:この女、ホントに僕を守る気があるんだろうか。[linebreak]いや、きっとないね。このビルに乗り込むとか言い出した時点で、僕は危険にさらされてるんだから。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:Was she really going to protect me? No, probably not. She was putting me in danger by forcing me to come here.[%p]"

msgid "4400:っていうか勝手に先に行かないでほしい。[linebreak]せめてどこへ行って、なにをしようとしているのか[linebreak]説明ぐらいしてくれ……。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:Also, please don't go on ahead without me! At least tell me where we're going, and what we're doing here![%p]"

msgid "4500:だいたい、なんでエレベーターじゃなくて階段なんだ。[linebreak]僕は運動は苦手なのに。[%p]"
msgstr "4500:And why do we need to take the stairs instead of the elevator? I'm out of shape.[%p]"

msgid "4600:[name]セナ[line]「エレベーターに乗るのは自殺行為だ」[%p]"
msgstr "4600:[name]セナ[line]Taking the elevators is suicide.[%p]"

msgid "4700:セナの声が上から響いてくる。[linebreak]また心を読まれた？[linebreak]僕はため息をつき、セナを追って階段に足を踏み出す。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:I could hear Sena's voice above me. More mind-reading? I sighed and followed Sena up the stairs.[%p]"

msgid "4800:２階まで上がるとそこでセナが待っていた。[linebreak]僕が追いついてきたのを見てから、また上っていく。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:When I got to the 2nd floor, Sena was waiting for me. When she saw that I'd caught up, she headed up another flight.[%p]"

msgid "4900:[name]セナ[line]「敵の本拠地でエレベーターに乗ったら、閉じ込められて身動きが取れなくなるのがオチだろ？」[%p]"
msgstr "4900:[name]セナ[line]If you try to use the elevator in the enemy's headquarters, they'll just lock you in and trap you, right?[%p]"

msgid "5000:[name]拓巳[line]「そ、それは、そうだけど……」[%p]"
msgstr "5000:[name]拓巳[line]Yeah, but...[%p]"

msgid "5100:[name]セナ[line]「それより西條。『将軍』について教えろ。そいつはいつからお前を攻撃するようになった？」[%p]"
msgstr "5100:[name]セナ[line]More importantly, Nishijo. Tell me about Shogun. When did he start coming after you?[%p]"

msgid "5200:[name]拓巳[line]「１ヶ月ぐらい、ま、前から……」[%p]"
msgstr "5200:[name]拓巳[line]A-About a month ago.[%p]"

msgid "5300:[name]セナ[line]「話したことがあるんだな？」[%p]"
msgstr "5300:[name]セナ[line]You've spoken to him, right?[%p]"

msgid "5400:うなずくと、セナは一度立ち止まり、上から僕を振り返った。[linebreak]パンツ見えそうな角度ですぞ、セナさん……。[linebreak]僕は反射的に目をそらした。[%p]"
msgstr "5400:I nodded. She turned around and looked down at me from above. I can almost see your panties from here, Sena. I quickly looked away.[%p]"

msgid "5500:[name]セナ[line]「どんなことを言っていた？」[%p]"
msgstr "5500:[name]セナ[line]What did he tell you?[%p]"

msgid "5600:どんなことって……。[linebreak]とりあえずこれまでの『将軍』の発言や、狂言誘拐で脅されたことについて、セナに話してみた。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:What did he tell me? I told her all about the things Shogun had told me, and about how he'd threatened me with a fake kidnapping.[%p]"

msgid "5700:[name]セナ[line]「……波多野、という名前に聞き覚えは？」[%p]"
msgstr "5700:[name]セナ[line]Have you ever heard the name Hatano?[%p]"

msgid "5800:[name]拓巳[line]「……ないけど」[%p]"
msgstr "5800:[name]拓巳[line]No, why?[%p]"

msgid "5900:[name]セナ[line]「『将軍』が言っていたかもしれないだろ。よく思い出せ」[%p]"
msgstr "5900:[name]セナ[line]Shogun might've said it, right? Think.[%p]"

msgid "6000:波多野……？[linebreak]分からない。[%p]"
msgstr "6000:Hatano? I hadn't heard it before.[%p]"

msgid "6100:[name]拓巳[line]「だ、誰？」[%p]"
msgstr "6100:[name]拓巳[line]W-Who's that?[%p]"

msgid "6200:[name]セナ[line]「プロジェクト・ノアにかかわっていた男だ」[%p]"
msgstr "6200:[name]セナ[line]Someone involved with Project Noah.[%p]"

msgid "6300:知らない。プロジェクト・ノアっていう言葉さえ、僕は分からないのに。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:I didn't know him. I didn't even know what Project Noah was.[%p]"

msgid "6400:[name]セナ[line]「……そうか。知らないなら別にいい」[%p]"
msgstr "6400:[name]セナ[line]I see. If you don't know, then that's fine.[%p]"

msgid "6500:セナはプイと顔をそらし、今度は黙って階段を上り始めた。[%p]"
msgstr "6500:She turned away from me and began to silently walk up the stairs.[%p]"

msgid "6600:[name]拓巳[line]「はあ、はあ……ま、まだ……？」[%p]"
msgstr "6600:[name]拓巳[line]Hahh... Hahh... A-Are we there yet?[%p]"

msgid "6700:ほぼ休みなしで２０階ぐらいまで来た。[linebreak]こんなに階段をたくさん上ったのは、初めてかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "6700:We'd walked up almost twenty flights of stairs with no break. I didn't think I'd ever walked up so many flights of stairs in my life.[%p]"

msgid "6800:疲れた……もう上りたくない……。[linebreak]額から汗が垂れて、目に入りそうになる。手で拭いても拭いても、汗はにじんでくる。足がだるくて、息も苦しくて窒息しそう。[%p]"
msgstr "6800:I was so tired... Please, no more stairs. The sweat was falling from my brow and threatening to get into my eyes. I kept wiping it away, and it kept coming back. My legs were exhausted, and I was so out of breath I thought I'd suffocate.[%p]"

msgid "6900:その場で膝に手を突き、息を整えようとしてみた。[linebreak]垂れた汗が、床に染みを作る。[%p]"
msgstr "6900:I bent over, hands on my knees, and tried to catch my breath. The sweat fell off and made a puddle on the floor.[%p]"

msgid "7000:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、あと、どれ、ぐらい、登るの……？」[%p]"
msgstr "7000:[name]拓巳[line]H-How many more flights to go?[%p]"

msgid "7100:[name]セナ[line]「社長室は最上階にあるらしい。３１階だ」[%p]"
msgstr "7100:[name]セナ[line]The CEO's office is supposed to be on the top floor. That would be the thirty-first.[%p]"

msgid "7200:あと１０階以上も登るのか……。[%p]"
msgstr "7200:Ten more flights of stairs?[%p]"

msgid "7300:って言うか、なんで僕はこんなことをしてるんだ。[linebreak]セナに“守ってくれ”って頼んだはずなのに、意味が分からないぞ。[linebreak]僕の脳裏にポルポルくんの顔が浮かんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "7300:Wait, why was I doing this? I'd asked Sena to protect me. What was I doing up here? I saw that ASCII art of Polnareff's face appear in my mind's eye. “You're right, I don't know what's going on at all.”[%p]"

msgid "7400:ハァハァ、という僕の荒い息が、静かな非常階段に響いている。[linebreak]セナは今度は意外にも先に行こうとはしなかった。[linebreak]壁に背を預け、僕を無表情で眺めている。[%p]"
msgstr "7400:The sound of my panting echoed through the quiet emergency staircase. Surprisingly, Sena didn't try to go on without me. She leaned up against the wall, staring at me expressionlessly.[%p]"

msgid "7500:どうやら少し休んでもいいってことらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:She was giving me a chance to rest, from the look of it.[%p]"

msgid "7600:そのセナの頭上には、例によって監視カメラ。[%p]"
msgstr "7600:There was another security camera above her head.[%p]"

msgid "7700:すべての階に設置されていた。[linebreak]きっと僕らがこの階段にいることは、とっくにバレているはずだ。[linebreak]そのうち、守衛が来るかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "7700:There were cameras on all the floors. They must've known exactly where we were for a while now. Security might come for us any moment.[%p]"

msgid "7800:[name]セナ[line]「監視カメラに細工をしなかったのは――」[%p]"
msgstr "7800:[name]セナ[line]The reason I didn't do anything to the cameras...[%p]"

msgid "7900:不意にセナがつぶやく。[%p]"
msgstr "7900:She whispered suddenly.[%p]"

msgid "8000:[name]セナ[line]「『将軍』がもし希の人間で、このビル内にいるなら、おびき寄せることができるかもしれないと思ったからだ」[%p]"
msgstr "8000:[name]セナ[line]...was that if Shogun, or anyone with Nozomi, was here, I wanted to lure them out.[%p]"

msgid "8100:[name]拓巳[line]「つ、つまり、ぼ、僕はおとりってわけ……？」[%p]"
msgstr "8100:[name]拓巳[line]I-In other words, I'm bait?[%p]"

msgid "8200:[name]セナ[line]「そういうことになる」[%p]"
msgstr "8200:[name]セナ[line]That's right.[%p]"

msgid "8300:[name]セナ[line]「もともと希になんか、興味はなかったんだけどな。このビルに乗り込むことにしたのだって、イレギュラーだ」[%p]"
msgstr "8300:[name]セナ[line]I was never interested in Nozomi in the first place. I wasn't planning on coming here, either.[%p]"

msgid "8400:[name]セナ[line]「もちろん、いつかはプロジェクト・ノアを潰そうとは思っていたが、それは今じゃない。それよりも優先しなくちゃいけないことがあった」[%p]"
msgstr "8400:[name]セナ[line]Of course, I was planning on destroying Project Noah at some point. But not now. There was something I had to do first.[%p]"

msgid "8500:急に饒舌になったけど……これってもしかして、ここに乗り込んだ理由について、説明してくれているんだろうか。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:She'd turned talkative all of a sudden... Maybe she was explaining the reason she'd come here?[%p]"

msgid "8600:セナは“優先しなくちゃいけないこと”については話さなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "8600:She didn't tell me what it was that she'd had to do first.[%p]"

msgid "8700:[name]セナ[line]「お前の話を聞く限り、その『将軍』はなにかを知ってる。あるいは、波多野のことも……」[%p]"
msgstr "8700:[name]セナ[line]From what you said, this Shogun seems to know something. He might know about Hatano.[%p]"

msgid "8800:その名前を口にするとき、セナの表情は一瞬だけ険しくなる。[linebreak]よっぽどの極悪人なのかな？[%p]"
msgstr "8800:Whenever she said the name, her expression would darken for a moment. Was he some kind of terrible criminal or something?[%p]"

msgid "8900:[name]セナ[line]「……安心しろ、西條。これは交換条件だ。お前におとりになってもらう代わりに、私はお前を守る」[%p]"
msgstr "8900:[name]セナ[line]Don't worry, Nishijo. We're making a fair trade. You're being my bait. And in exchange, I'll protect you.[%p]"

msgid "9000:[name]セナ[line]「それにお前だって、『将軍』の正体を知りたいだろ？\u3000脅威を排除するにはこちらから攻撃――」[%p]"
msgstr "9000:[name]セナ[line]And you want to know who Shogun really is, right? If you want to get rid of a threat, the best thing to do is go on the offensive, and—[%p]"

msgid "9100:不意にセナは口をつぐんだ。[linebreak]不思議そうに眉根を寄せる。壁に預けていた背中を離し、この狭い踊り場で、長大なディソードを構える。[%p]"
msgstr "9100:She suddenly stopped speaking. Her eyes narrowed. She stepped away from the wall, holding her Di-Sword at the ready on the small landing.[%p]"

msgid "9200:[name]拓巳[line]「ど、どうしたの……？」[%p]"
msgstr "9200:[name]拓巳[line]W-What's wrong?[%p]"

msgid "9300:[name]セナ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "9300:[name]セナ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "9400:セナは答えてくれない。[linebreak]階段の下の方をのぞき込み、それから上を見上げ――[linebreak]そこで動きが止まった。[%p]"
msgstr "9400:Sena didn't answer. She looked down over the stair railing, and then up. And then froze.[%p]"

msgid "9500:[name]セナ[line]「この声……どこから……？」[%p]"
msgstr "9500:[name]セナ[line]Where is this voice coming from?[%p]"

msgid "9600:声……？[%p]"
msgstr "9600:Voice?[%p]"

msgid "9700:[name]セナ[line]「お前、何者だっ！」[%p]"
msgstr "9700:[name]セナ[line]Who are you!?[%p]"

msgid "9800:いきなり叫ぶ。[linebreak]てっきり監視カメラに対して吠えているのかと思ったけど、視線はもっと上……天井に向いていた。[%p]"
msgstr "9800:She suddenly screamed. I thought she was yelling at the cameras, but she was looking further up, at the ceiling.[%p]"

msgid "9900:まさか――[%p]"
msgstr "9900:Was it...[%p]"

msgid "10000:イヤな予感がした。[linebreak]僕も釣られて天井を見上げた。[linebreak]当然ながらなにもない。[%p]"
msgstr "10000:A terrible thought ran through my mind. I looked up too, Of course, there was nothing there.[%p]"

msgid "10100:それに僕には“声”は聞こえない。[linebreak]でも、なんとなく予想はついた。[%p]"
msgstr "10100:And I couldn't hear a voice, either. I could tell what was going on, though.[%p]"

msgid "10200:『将軍』だ……！[linebreak]ヤツが、はるか上空の人工衛星から思考盗撮をしていて、“声”を聞かせているんだ！[%p]"
msgstr "10200:Shogun! He was using satellites in the sky far above us to read her mind, and speak to her![%p]"

msgid "10300:[name]拓巳[line]「セ、セナ！\u3000その声を、聞いちゃ、ダメだ……っ！」[%p]"
msgstr "10300:[name]拓巳[line]S-Sena! Don't listen to that voice![%p]"

msgid "10400:[name]セナ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "10400:[name]セナ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "10500:[name]拓巳[line]「セナ！」[%p]"
msgstr "10500:[name]拓巳[line]Sena![%p]"

msgid "10600:とっさに肩をつかみ、揺さぶる。[%p]"
msgstr "10600:I grabbed her and shook her.[%p]"

msgid "10700:[name]セナ[line]「……『将軍』は、希の人間じゃないらしい」[%p]"
msgstr "10700:[name]セナ[line]It looks like Shogun isn't working with Nozomi.[%p]"

msgid "10800:やっぱりだ……！[linebreak]『将軍』の声をセナは聞いたんだ！[%p]"
msgstr "10800:I knew it! Sena had heard Shogun's voice![%p]"

msgid "10900:[name]拓巳[line]「だ、だ、騙されてるっ！\u3000あいつは、て、敵だよっ！\u3000し、信じちゃ、ダメだ……っ！」[%p]"
msgstr "10900:[name]拓巳[line]H-He's lying to you! He's my e-enemy! D-Don't believe him![%p]"

msgid "11000:[name]セナ[line]「音だ……」[%p]"
msgstr "11000:[name]セナ[line]The sound...[%p]"

msgid "11100:[name]拓巳[line]「……え？」[%p]"
msgstr "11100:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "11200:セナの肩にかけていた僕の手。[linebreak]その手首を、逆にきつくつかまれた。[linebreak]爪が食い込んで、走る痛み。[%p]"
msgstr "11200:My hand was on her shoulder. She grabbed it and held it tight. Her nails dug into me. It hurt.[%p]"

msgid "11300:僕は顔をしかめ――[%p]"
msgstr "11300:I winced—[%p]"

msgid "11400:[name]セナ[line]「西條、音がしている！\u3000気を付けろ――」[%p]"
msgstr "11400:[name]セナ[line]Nishijo, that's the sound! Be careful![%p]"

msgid "11500:頭の中で、閃光が爆ぜた。[linebreak]浮かび上がったのは、映像。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:There was a flash of light above us. I saw an image in my mind.[%p]"

msgid "11600:暗い部屋。[linebreak]床にできた、血溜まり。[linebreak]十字架のようなオブジェ。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:A dark room. A pool of blood on the floor. A strange object that looked like a cross.[%p]"

msgid "11700:そこに拘束され、力なくうなだれているのは――[linebreak]服を血に染めた――[linebreak]右の手首を無残に切断された――[%p]"
msgstr "11700:And someone lying helpless, trapped, bound to it. Their clothes stained with blood. Their right hand severed at the wrist...[%p]"

msgid "11800:[name]拓巳[line]「――わああああっ！」[%p]"
msgstr "11800:[name]拓巳[line]Waaah![%p]"

msgid "11900:見えた――[%p]"
msgstr "11900:I saw it...[%p]"

msgid "12000:はっきり、見えた。[linebreak]今のは、間違いなく。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:I could see every detail. I was sure of who I'd seen.[%p]"

msgid "12100:七海だ。[%p]"
msgstr "12100:It was Nanami.[%p]"

msgid "12200:[name]拓巳[line]「な、な、七海がっ！\u3000なな、七海が、こ、このビルの、どこかに！」[%p]"
msgstr "12200:[name]拓巳[line]N-Nanami! Nana... Nanami is somewhere in this building![%p]"

msgid "12300:やっぱり『将軍』に連れ去られていたんだ！[linebreak]手首だって、妄想なんかじゃなくて、ホントだったんだ！[%p]"
msgstr "12300:Shogun had kidnapped her after all! The severed hand was real, not a delusion![%p]"

msgid "12400:探さないと……。[%p]"
msgstr "12400:I had to find her.[%p]"

msgid "12500:あのとき、僕が助けてあげられなかったせいで、今も七海は苦しんでるんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:I hadn't been able to save her, and now she was suffering.[%p]"

msgid "12600:だから、探さないと。[linebreak]今度こそ、僕がなんとかしないと……。[%p]"
msgstr "12600:I had to find her. This time, I had to save her![%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]セナ[line]「落ち着け、西條！\u3000これは罠の可能性が――」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]セナ[line]Calm down, Nishijo! It might be a trap—[%p]"

msgid "12800:[name]拓巳[line]「さ、さっき、君だって、し、『将軍』の言葉を信じたじゃないか！」[%p]"
msgstr "12800:[name]拓巳[line]W-Well, y-you just believed what Shogun said, didn't you?[%p]"

msgid "12900:僕はセナの手を強引に振り払った。[linebreak]社長室は、３１階だったよな……。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:I knocked Sena's hand away. The CEO's office was on the thirty-first floor, right?[%p]"

msgid "13000:[name]セナ[line]「違う、音を聞け！『将軍』の干渉とは別の妄想だ！」[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[name]セナ[line]No! Listen to the sound! It's a different delusion than the one Shogun was using![%p]"

msgid "13100:無視して、駆け上がる。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:I ignored her and started to run.[%p]"

msgid "13200:疲れただなんて弱音を吐いてる場合じゃなかった。[linebreak]必死だった。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:I was tired, but it didn't matter. I was desperate.[%p]"

msgid "13300:七海が苦しんでいる。[linebreak]僕のせいだ。全部、僕のせいなんだ。[linebreak]あのときはダメだった。僕は逃げた。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:Nanami was suffering. It was my fault... It was all my fault. I'd failed last time. I'd run away.[%p]"

msgid "13400:七海に恨まれる。[linebreak]許して……。[linebreak]僕は最低の兄貴だ……。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:Nanami must hate me. Forgive me... I'm such a terrible brother.[%p]"

msgid "13500:ちくしょう、力がほしい。セナみたいに、ディソードがほしい。[linebreak]なんで僕は、ディソードを手に入れられないんだ。[linebreak]こんなに求めてるのに……。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:Damn it... I wanted power. A Di-Sword, like Sena had. Why couldn't I get a Di-Sword? I wanted it so badly.[%p]"

msgid "13600:七海、死ぬな……。[linebreak]頼むから……。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:Nanami, don't die. Please...[%p]"

